{"tid":254227,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫耶斯辭職唔要3千萬　傑斯等接班 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2017-05-23T04:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T11:20:56.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf76695e9dd7e55c8661f3a0f8f596f86d1b96b","tid":254227,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"新特蘭領隊莫耶斯，於英國時間周一下晝決定辭職，結束10個月執教黑貓生涯。早前有傳佢矢志親手將黑貓帶番上英超，但最後決定離開。佢於舊年夏天同新特蘭簽約4年，依家教得1季就走，照計可以攞番300萬鎊（約3000萬港元）賠償，但拒絕接受，新特蘭主席伊利斯索治盛讚佢有性格。<br />\n<br />\n新特蘭本季表現乏善足陳，莫耶斯帶隊43場，只係贏得8仗，勝率僅得18.6%，球隊最後包尾降班，莫天才當然被受評擊，相信佢本人都覺得有負球隊，故選擇放棄巨款離開。伊利斯索治表示，莫耶斯上季為黑貓盡心盡力，但始終未能救球隊於水火，今次決定提早解約，絕對值得攞番賠償，但莫耶斯決定放棄，係有性格嘅表現。英媒表示，傑斯好可能接任黑貓領隊，有當地博彩公司，將佢列為接任熱門之一，賠率為5.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n傑斯咪又係師承椰子'<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_45.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_45.gif&h=22f7bd8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3c81d59e6d01eb37de9d9a4758e17e5a34e568","tid":254227,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"然後敢帥教😱"},{"pid":"083363550eccbcb394a19fd71ad7fefd73cf3852","tid":254227,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"岩啦<br />\n傑斯教j仔睇下仲可唔可以成材"},{"pid":"e8ad4011b8045147d123c354ac6d55dd6d857d04","tid":254227,"uid":33443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"Barcelona will name new Coach on May 29th<br />\n耶子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aef8a0dc3a8aac81b780c58d72bb34da81f83d8","tid":254227,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Barcelona will name new Coach on May 29th<br />\n耶子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a371764ed670a